'''啮虫目'''（學名：{{lang|la|Psocodea}}）是由傳統分類的[[啮虫目|啮虫目]]（亦有簡化作'''𪘅目'''<ref>{{cite book |title=《中國𪘅目誌》 |author=[[李法圣|李法圣]] |url=http://www.amazon.cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD-lt-%E8%99%AB%E9%BD%BF-gt-%E7%9B%AE%E5%BF%97-%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%A3/dp/B00114NN62 |date=2002-01-01 |accessdate=2015-01-28 |publisher=[[中國科學出版社|中國科學出版社]] |language=zh-hans |isbn=9787030091734 |archive-date=2015-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204150656/http://www.amazon.cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD-lt-%E8%99%AB%E9%BD%BF-gt-%E7%9B%AE%E5%BF%97-%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%A3/dp/B00114NN62 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）、[[裸尾目|裸尾目]]及[[食毛目|食毛目]]三個目合併而成<ref name="Gullan">{{cite book |author=P. J. Gullan & P. S. Cranston |year=2010 |title=The Insects: an Outline of Entomology |edition=4th |publisher=[[約翰威立|John Wiley & Sons]] |isbn=9781444317671 |page=479 |chapter=Taxobox 17 – Psocodea: "Psocoptera" (bark lice and book lice) |url={{google books |id=S7yGZasJ7nEC |pg=PA479 |plain-url=yes}} |access-date=2015-04-08 |archive-date=2015-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421223146/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=S7yGZasJ7nEC&pg=PA479 |dead-url=no |language=en}}</ref>。過往的分類認為本分類單元是[[昆虫纲|昆虫纲]]的一个总目，但到了2020年代，學界的共識是它應該是[[新翅下綱|新翅下綱]]的一個目級分類<ref name=Johnson2021 /><ref name=DeMoya2021 />。儘管這個新分類的物種間形態分別很大，研究指出牠們其實都是從傳統分類的啮虫目演化而成<ref>{{cite journal |author=C. H. C. Lyal |year=1985 |title=Phylogeny and classification of the Psocodea, with particular reference to the lice (Psocodea: Phthiraptera) |journal={{tsl|en|Systematic Entomology||Systematic Entomology}} |volume=10 |issue=2 |pages=145–165 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-3113.1985.tb00525.x}}</ref>。這個合併後的新啮虫目合共有約1.1萬個物種，按各自原來所屬的亞目分類，合共7個亞目<ref name="Gullan"/><ref>{{cite book |author={{tsl|en|David Grimaldi (entomologist)||David Grimaldi}} & {{tsl|en|Michael S. Engel||Michael S. Engel}} |year=2005 |title=Evolution of the Insects |series=Cambridge Evolution Series |publisher=[[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]] |isbn=9780521821490 |chapter=The paraneopteran orders |pages=216–330 |url={{google books |id=Ql6Jl6wKb88C |pg=PA261 |plain-url=yes}} |access-date=2015-04-08 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209135158/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=Ql6Jl6wKb88C&pg=PA261 |dead-url=no |page=261 |language=en}}</ref>。

==概說==
本目學名「Psocodea」一词来源于[[希腊语|希腊语]]的''psokos''({{lang|el|ψωκος}})，意为“啮，咬”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cals.ncsu.edu/course/ent425/compendium/psocop~1.html |title=Psocoptera |publisher=[[北卡罗来纳州立大学|North Carolina State University]] |author=John R. Meyer |date=2005-03-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070205021919/http://www.cals.ncsu.edu/course/ent425/compendium/psocop~1.html |archivedate=2007-02-05 |accessdate=2015-01-22 }}</ref>，所以本目又稱為'''咀顎目'''。

原啮虫目的动物，俗称'''书虱'''、'''米虱'''，包含了室內的書蝨及野外的樹蝨<ref name=nchu>{{cite web |url=http://www.entomol.nchu.edu.tw/dept/teachers/jtyang/article/T4Bio20120529.pdf |title=昆蟲分類學-科博館參訪心得 |date=2012-05-29 |publisher=[[中興大學|中興大學]]昆蟲學系 |author=梁維仁 |accessdate=2014-08-30 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2020-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006040523/http://www.entomol.nchu.edu.tw/dept/teachers/jtyang/article/T4Bio20120529.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。体长在1毫米至1厘米之间。啮虫目出现于2.95亿年至2.48亿年前。[[蝨毛目|蝨毛目]]是[[原蝨目|原蝨目]]和[[食毛目|食毛目]]的合稱，通稱'''虱'''或'''虱子'''全世界約有3,000種。到了2000年代後期，根據[[分子生物學|分子生物學]]及[[形態學_(生物學)|形態學]]對[[絲角亞目|絲角亞目]]物種的研究，確認了蝨毛目與原啮虫目是近親，而蝨毛目其實是從[[粉啮虫亚目|粉啮虫亚目]]演變而成的<ref>{{cite journal |last=Yoshizawa |first=K. |first2=K. P. |last2=Johnson |year=2006 |title= Morphology of male genitalia in lice and their relatives and phylogenetic implications |journal=Systematic Entomology |volume=31 |issue=2 |pages=350–361 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-3113.2005.00323.x }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Johnson |first=K. P. |last2=Yoshizawa |first2=K. |first3=V. S. |last3=Smith |year=2004 |title=Multiple origins of parasitism in lice |journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_Royal_Society_of_London|Proceedings of the Royal Society of London]] |volume=271 |issue=1550 |pages=1771–1776 |doi=10.1098/rspb.2004.2798 |pmid=15315891 |pmc=1691793}}</ref>，因此建議重組這兩個目<ref name=nchu /><ref>Bess, Emilie, Vince Smith, Charles Lienhard, and Kevin P. Johnson (2006) Psocodea. Parasitic Lice (=Phthiraptera), Book Lice, and Bark Lice. Version 8 October 2006 (under construction). http://tolweb.org/Psocodea/8235/2006.10.08 {{Wayback|url=http://tolweb.org/Psocodea/8235/2006.10.08 |date=20201006040528 }} in The Tree of Life Web Project, http://tolweb.org/ {{Wayback|url=http://tolweb.org/ |date=20110515100516 }}</ref>。

